EmailTemplate.subject: Order Confirmation (Partner 'sName) PO #, SO #
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello (Name of Partner),
This email is to acknowledge the Purchase Order we received on (date.)
PO Name: Sales Order Acknowledgement No#: (Screen Shot List of items here.)
If any of the information listed appears incorrect, please contact us immediately. We will take your request and provide response shortly on material availability of your preferred delivery.
Note: Unless objection is received within 3 days of receipt of this notification it shall be taken that you agree with sales order content and the terms and conditions stated in Australia Partner Price List (001-61270).
Let us know should you have any concerns.
Regards, {!User.Username} Partner Service Representative
